Comment: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dammit, we fell for it! It was after the magic stones\Nof the monsters that we defeated all along!
Comment: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,An Undine Cloth!
Comment: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It stole from dead adventurers!
Comment: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:51.82,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Which means that if the scales\Ndon't start to tip in our favor after using it...
Comment: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:30.56,Flashback,,0,0,0,,We're about to enter the lower floors, which are\Nsomething that even we don't have experience with.
Comment: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What about shooting some arrows, or using that\NLevel Boost from earlier? There has to be a way to help!
Dialogue: 99,0:00:06.15,0:00:10.16,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Isso é... um grimório.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:10.16,0:00:11.37,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Claro.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:11.37,0:00:15.54,Flashback,,0,0,0,,É um item muito conveniente que pode\Nforçar o despertar de novas magias em quem o lê.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:16.29,0:00:19.50,Flashback,,0,0,0,,É claro, não há como saber exatamente\Nque tipo de magia será.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:19.75,0:00:24.63,Flashback,,0,0,0,,B-Bem... um item tão precioso\Nnão seria desperdiçado comigo...
Dialogue: 99,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.38,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Pensei que tinha sido claro.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:26.80,0:00:30.34,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Você vai ser um peso para a festa \Nse fornecer um aumento de nível for a única coisa que você pode fazer.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:31.59,0:00:33.60,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Não importa qual mágica você obtenha.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:33.60,0:00:35.64,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Pode ser um feitiço de cura ou um feitiço de ataque.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:35.64,0:00:37.56,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Apenas leia isso e expanda seu conjunto de habilidades.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:38.10,0:00:40.77,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Porque qualquer coisa pode salvar a vida dos seus amigos.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:41.90,0:00:45.98,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Se você realmente quer defender sua Familia, \Nentão faça o que for preciso.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:46.23,0:00:47.74,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Esqueça o que os outros pensam.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:47.74,0:00:49.99,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Deixe-se ser ganancioso e jogar sujo.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:49.99,0:00:52.32,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Vá em frente. Apresse-se e leia isso.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:52.32,0:00:55.20,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Entao podemos praticar sua nova magica.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:56.66,0:00:57.70,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem.
